title: Leadership Development
description: Developing the knowledge, skills, and experience needed to lead others in achieving a common goal or outcome.

title: Career and Professional Development
description: Engaging in programs and activities that help one to formulate well-developed career goals and to develop competitive skills and experiences for future employment or acceptance into graduate or professional school.

title: Communication Skills
description: Becoming an effective communicator by developing and sharpening one's oral, nonverbal, interpersonal, and written communication skills.

title: Cross-Functional Team Management
description: Strengthening your ability to be a valuable contributor to cross-functional teams through collaboration, information sharing, teamwork, decision making, and effective followership.

title: Personal Financial Literacy and Wellness
description: Understanding how money and capital works, how to earn and manage it.
